=C2=A0

Trump looms over every decision in town, of course, and that comprises the =
theme of tonight=E2=80=99s email. John Heilemann has
a candid conversation with former Obama administration and Hillary campaign=
 comms director Jen Palmieri about the Democrats in the wilderness, the bro=
